  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of vegetable oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add onion and garlic and sauté until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add tomato puree, wine, and coconut cream. Stir to combine.",
    "Let the mixture simmer for 10 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Meanwhile, preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Place the bao dough on a baking sheet and bake for 10 minutes, or until crispy.",
    "Remove the bao from the oven and split them open.",
    "Fill each bao with the tomato cream mixture and top with cilantro, salt, pepper, and nutritional yeast.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
